Hey, what are you staring at?

530
00:41:55,513 --> 00:41:56,931
You're young and strong.

531
00:41:57,014 --> 00:42:00,100
Come out of there
and help us carry all of this, huh?

532
00:42:01,018 --> 00:42:01,936
Hey.

533
00:42:08,192 --> 00:42:11,862
-Keep them separate, then count.
-Wow, the rich do live differently, huh?

534
00:42:11,946 --> 00:42:13,989
There, there, there.

535
00:42:14,073 --> 00:42:16,700
Oh, Sister,
can you lend me a hand?

536
00:42:16,784 --> 00:42:18,202
Look at all the stuff!

537
00:42:18,285 --> 00:42:21,997
-I know. We finally have rice again.
-That's the last of the rice.

538
00:42:22,081 --> 00:42:24,833
-Should we finish dividing it?
-He'll come.

539
00:42:26,085 --> 00:42:27,461
My son will come.

540
00:42:27,545 --> 00:42:28,879
I know he will.

541
00:42:29,964 --> 00:42:33,467
-That's what he said before he--
-You saw the news, didn't you?

542
00:42:36,679 --> 00:42:39,515
This must be divine punishment, isn't it?

543
00:42:39,598 --> 00:42:40,641
Yeah.

544
00:42:41,141 --> 00:42:42,810
Your mistakes led you here.

545
00:42:42,893 --> 00:42:45,229
You created a lot of suffering
for everyone.

546
00:42:45,312 --> 00:42:47,773
You made my grandma's life so difficult.

547
00:42:51,026 --> 00:42:53,821
I lived my life wrong, didn't I?

548
00:42:53,904 --> 00:42:58,742
Even so, I thought I'd at least
raised my own son not to.

549
00:43:00,327 --> 00:43:01,745
It's all right.

550
00:43:04,373 --> 00:43:05,958
None of us have been abandoned.

551
00:43:07,293 --> 00:43:08,335
Huh?

552
00:43:09,837 --> 00:43:11,880
Instead, everyone here survived.

553
00:43:23,017 --> 00:43:24,184
What do you think?

554
00:43:24,268 --> 00:43:26,520
This place is pretty big.
Think it'll be enough?

555
00:43:27,021 --> 00:43:28,606
Yeah, this is great.

556
00:43:29,273 --> 00:43:31,483
Thanks for arranging this place for me.

557
00:43:31,567 --> 00:43:33,819
Of course. I'm happy to help.

558
00:43:39,033 --> 00:43:40,034
Yun-sang,

559
00:43:41,493 --> 00:43:43,621
this project of yours sounds pretty fun.

560
00:43:45,623 --> 00:43:49,960
You writing down everyone's stories.
It's like a time capsule.

561
00:43:51,503 --> 00:43:54,006
Yeah, I've been coming up
with fun ideas for our town.

562
00:43:55,007 --> 00:43:57,509
I have a few others in mind, too,
for my spare time.

563
00:43:57,593 --> 00:44:01,639
You know, I'm not sure you'll have any.
Over 200 people have already applied.

564
00:44:01,722 --> 00:44:02,681
Huh?

565
00:44:02,765 --> 00:44:05,684
Take your time looking around.

566
00:44:07,853 --> 00:44:10,189
Oh. Ah, hello.

567
00:44:11,482 --> 00:44:13,692
Do you have
the documents I asked for last time?

568
00:44:13,776 --> 00:44:15,319
I'll have them ready
by this afternoon.

569
00:44:15,402 --> 00:44:17,655
The afternoon?
Sure, there's no need to rush.

570
00:44:21,283 --> 00:44:23,994
-Have you eaten?
-Oh, it's all right.

571
00:44:24,828 --> 00:44:26,330
I'll have some lunch later.

572
00:44:35,464 --> 00:44:37,800
-What did you think?
-That was amazing.

573
00:44:37,883 --> 00:44:38,759
Oh, hello.

574
00:44:39,760 --> 00:44:41,011
It's cold today.

575
00:44:41,512 --> 00:44:43,931
Hello. Oh, you came!

576
00:44:44,014 --> 00:44:47,101
-I had a craving for this.
-The hand-pulled dough soup is amazing.

577
00:44:47,184 --> 00:44:48,977
Wait, wait, wait. Come over here.

578
00:44:49,478 --> 00:44:50,979
-Hello.
-Hello, Sister.

579
00:44:51,480 --> 00:44:52,940
Have you heard the news?

580
00:44:53,691 --> 00:44:55,109
It's about Father Woo.

581
00:45:20,259 --> 00:45:22,302
Father? It's time to eat.

582
00:45:34,189 --> 00:45:37,568
From now on, you don't have to worry
about bringing me my meals.

583
00:45:37,651 --> 00:45:40,612
Starting today, I'll manage the church
as just a layperson.

584
00:45:40,696 --> 00:45:41,613
Lay--

585
00:45:42,740 --> 00:45:43,824
Layperson?

586
00:45:44,616 --> 00:45:45,951
Manage the church?

587
00:45:47,828 --> 00:45:49,621
I already sent in my resignation.

588
00:45:51,874 --> 00:45:53,083
Father!

589
00:45:53,792 --> 00:45:57,254
Please, Father. Father!
Father, this isn't right at all!

590
00:45:57,337 --> 00:45:59,214
There's no way
the parish elders would allow it!

591
00:45:59,298 --> 00:46:00,799
What parish elders?

592
00:46:01,300 --> 00:46:03,218
The bishop and the head nun
are in a nursing home.

593
00:46:03,302 --> 00:46:05,304
Oh, Father, you can't! Please!

594
00:46:05,387 --> 00:46:07,347
How can you even think of doing this?

595
00:46:07,431 --> 00:46:08,682
I've been with you since…

596
00:46:08,766 --> 00:46:11,268
ever since you were
in seminary school, haven't I?

597
00:46:12,311 --> 00:46:14,813
I know you're very upset by this,
but I'm sorry.

598
00:46:14,897 --> 00:46:17,941
You can't! Father, you can't!
You just can't!

599
00:46:18,025 --> 00:46:19,568
Father! Father!

600
00:46:21,069 --> 00:46:23,572
Just what are we
supposed to do now, Yun-sang?

601
00:46:23,655 --> 00:46:24,698
This is a disaster!

602
00:46:24,782 --> 00:46:27,075
The Cheondong Church won't have a priest!

603
00:46:27,159 --> 00:46:29,119
Father, please!

604
00:46:32,539 --> 00:46:33,874
What's this about?

605
00:46:34,625 --> 00:46:36,543
You should've at least told me.

606
00:46:37,085 --> 00:46:39,922
Well, I thought
you would've guessed, Yun-sang.

607
00:46:43,258 --> 00:46:46,845
Another surprise stunt.
You love doing this, don't you?

608
00:46:46,929 --> 00:46:49,473
Surprise stunts? As if.

609
00:46:49,556 --> 00:46:53,018
What are you talking about?
You think I could plan anything right now?

610
00:46:54,144 --> 00:46:56,438
I guess, maybe not, but still…

611
00:46:57,773 --> 00:46:58,857
Oh, wait.

612
00:46:58,941 --> 00:47:00,067
What?

613
00:47:04,780 --> 00:47:05,864
Oh, hello.

614
00:47:09,952 --> 00:47:13,038
Did you… get any sleep last night?

615
00:47:14,581 --> 00:47:15,582
None.

616
00:47:19,753 --> 00:47:23,298
He kept repeating the same thing
over and over again all night.

617
00:47:24,591 --> 00:47:25,843
I was going insane.

618
00:47:27,761 --> 00:47:28,762
Hyung.

619
00:47:29,847 --> 00:47:32,975
